      "content": "sometimes i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize the person looking back. it’s not that i look old, it’s just that the person i actually was... the one with the dreams and the spark... that person died a long time ago. i feel like i'm just a walking corpse dragging around the shell of a life that doesn't belong to me anymore.",
