    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s not just buried though. i don’t think it’s even under the surface anymore. it’s just... gone. it’s like the life part of me finished its cycle and left, and now i’m just stuck inhabiting this body because it’s what’s left. i'm just going through the motions, but there's no one actually home. it feels so hollow.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
