    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't want to rebuild anything. that's the thing. rebuilding implies there's still something worth saving, but there isn't. it's like trying to fix a house that's already been gutted by fire. you're just standing in the ruins. why should i keep trying to patch up a shell that's already empty? it just feels like a waste of energy at this point.",
